The app compiles. Let me analyze the actual issue more carefully.

Looking at `main.js:94`:
```js
await getCurrentWindow().hide();
```

And in `main.js:116-119`:
```js
getCurrentWindow().onCloseRequested(async (event) => {
  event.preventDefault();
  await closeWindow();
});
```

The issue is that `onCloseRequested` might not be working correctly in Tauri v2. Let me check the Tauri version and the API:

